stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> unregistered: POST /assets (lifecycle=unregistered)
  [*] --> active: POST /assets (default lifecycle=active)

  unregistered --> active: PATCH lifecycle=active
  active --> deprecated: PATCH lifecycle=deprecated
  deprecated --> active: PATCH (re-activate, rare)
  deprecated --> sunset: PATCH lifecycle=sunset
  active --> sunset: PATCH (skip deprecated)
  sunset --> [*]: keep for history, no new versions expected

  note right of unregistered
    Planned but not ready.
    Versions can exist but
    should not be promoted.
  end note

  note right of active
    Production use allowed.
    Versions can be created
    and promoted normally.
  end note

  note right of deprecated
    Still functional.
    Discourage new integrations.
    Existing renders still work.
  end note

  note right of sunset
    Retired. Read-only.
    Kept for audit and history.
  end note
